itunes:title: MAY 30 2022 - THE NIGHT TRAIN TO ODESSA
title: MAY 30 2022 - THE NIGHT TRAIN TO ODESSA
description:
On today's special episode of Human Events Daily, Jack Posobiec takes you on the ground deep into Southern Ukraine. In all he and the crew traveled 1,200 miles by train and car, more than 40 hours from the border city of Lviv in the West, to blockaded Odessa on the Black Sea, and the besieged city of Mykolaiv. This episode was recorded while on the train between various points of the journey. 


Donations to Ukraine Humanistarian Aid: https://www.caritas.org/ukraine-appeal-22/
